reviewText: This film was very enjoyable. Twists and turns and a good tale. Alex Kingston's acting in this is above and beyond--she carries the film, and makes it look easy.
Very good movie. Did not expect the ending. Well played and thought out

I chose this movie because it starrerd Alex Kingston. She was a doctor in many years of the TV hit series, ER.  I wanted to see what else she had done.  Alex is from England, and has that delightful English accent.  I surely did love seeing her again, after watching the ER series.  I would recommend it to anyone who loved to see  her in the  ER  DVD movies.
Brilliant performances, especially Alex Kingston, and enough plot twists that I didn't guess them all. Solid film to watch and it's a shame it doesn't get more recognition.
